The Chicago Tribune's recent investigation <a href="http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/specials/chi-071205cops-htmlstory,0,4405016.htmlstory" target="_blank">"Shielded from the Truth"</a> is a devastating indictment of the CPD.<p>
